transcript.speaker: AI
transcript.text: Thank you for calling Conneverse Auto Repair! I'm here to help you with your vehicle service needs. May I have your name please?

transcript.speaker: user
transcript.text: Yes, my name is Sarah Johnson.

transcript.speaker: AI
transcript.text: Thank you, Sarah! Can you confirm the phone number you're calling from?

transcript.speaker: AI
transcript.text: Perfect! What vehicle do you need service for? Please tell me the year, make, and model.

transcript.speaker: AI
transcript.text: Got it, a 2019 Toyota RAV4. What seems to be the problem with your vehicle, or what service do you need?

transcript.speaker: user
transcript.text: I need new brake pads. I've been hearing a squeaking noise when I brake, especially at low speeds.

transcript.speaker: AI
transcript.text: I understand. That squeaking definitely needs attention. How soon do you need this taken care of? Is this urgent, or is the timing flexible?

transcript.speaker: user
transcript.text: I'd say it's pretty urgent. I use my car daily for work.

transcript.speaker: AI
transcript.text: Understood. So to summarize: Sarah Johnson, 2019 Toyota RAV4, needs brake pad replacement due to squeaking noise, and this is urgent. Is that correct?

transcript.speaker: AI
transcript.text: Perfect! We have all your information. Our team will review your case and get back to you shortly with a quote. Is there anything else you'd like to add before we go?

transcript.speaker: AI
transcript.text: Thank you for calling Conneverse Auto Repair, Sarah! We'll be in touch soon. Have a great day!

variables.notes: Customer reports squeaking noise when braking at low speeds. Uses vehicle daily for work commute.
